column5: Other than My Outdoortv.com where do you guys get your fishing fix from.  I just found a new site for all you fly fishers  SportFishing on the Fly.  20 minute episodes good action.  There is about 30 or 40 episodes I think    Thanks    Ian
Google "jazz and fly fishing" or "uncut angling" or go here... http://globalflyfisher.com/video/best
Facts of fishing , very entertaining half hour
Here for sure; a couple of other forums, and myoutdoortv, as well.
YouTube is pretty good but there's too many people with video titles that don't match the video...   ...
If I need a carp fishing fix...I just enter Korda carpfishing in Youtube search area...about 50 links come up...most for 45 minute sessions...
